{"type":"message","id":"3f45fbfd","parentId":"c4b7954d","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:04:04.631Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5d0ca12b4a474984a3ccbbb0","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"@ai-sdk/perplexity\nThe **[Perplexity provider](https://ai-sdk.dev/providers/ai-sdk-providers/perplexity)** for the [AI SDK](https://ai-sdk.dev/docs) contains language model support for Perplexity's Sonar API - a powerful answer engine with real-time web search capabilities.\nVersion 3.0.23 published 2026-03-05 by vercel-release-bot\nMaintainers: vercel-release-bot matheuss matt.straka\nKeywords: ai\nhttps://npm.im/@ai-sdk/perplexity\n\n@perplexity-ai/mcp-server\nReal-time web search, reasoning, and research through Perplexity's API\nVersion 0.8.3 published 2026-02-26 by GitHub Actions\nMaintainers: dan-pplx long-pplx jasonklym-pplx kesku\nKeywords: ai perplexity mcp modelcontextprotocol\nhttps://npm.im/@perplexity-ai/mcp-server\n\n@brave/brave-search-mcp-server\nBrave Search MCP Server: web results, images, videos, rich results, AI summaries, and more.\nVersion 2.0.75 published 2026-02-26 by brave.com\nMaintainers: bcrypt brianbondy brave.com darkdh mrose17 petemill pes10k jonathansampson antonok\nKeywords: api brave mcp search\nhttps://npm.im/@brave/brave-search-mcp-server\n\nweb-vitals\nEasily measure performance metrics in JavaScript\nVersion 5.1.0 published 2025-07-31 by tunetheweb\nMaintainers: philipwalton google-wombot tunetheweb\nKeywords: crux performance metrics Core Web Vitals CLS FCP INP LCP TTFB\nhttps://npm.im/web-vitals\n\n@tavily/n8n-nodes-tavily\nA community node for n8n to integrate Tavily API for web search and content extraction.\nVersion 0.5.1 published 2026-01-29 by mayramati\nMaintainers: konstantintzt carl-vbn guyhartstein michael_griff mayramati yashwanth-alapati\nKeywords: n8n-community-node-package\nhttps://npm.im/@tavily/n8n-nodes-tavily\n\nopencode-antigravity-auth\nGoogle Antigravity IDE OAuth auth plugin for Opencod