{"type":"message","id":"ee3613e4","parentId":"5ff53653","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:53:35.872Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"给用户一个简洁的“最新文档入口”和本地 docs 里最相关的入口即可。可以，先给你最快可用的入口。\n\n**OpenClaw 文档入口**\n- 本地文档目录：`/app/docs`\n- 在线文档：`https://docs.openclaw.ai`\n\n**我这边看到的文档分类里，比较常用的有：**\n- CLI 总览：`/app/docs/cli/index.md`\n- 配置：`/app/docs/cli/configure.md`\n- Gateway：`/app/docs/cli/gateway.md`\n- Channels：`/app/docs/channels/index.md`\n- Brave Search：`/app/docs/brave-search.md`\n- 自动化 / Cron：`/app/docs/automation/cron-jobs.md`\n- Heartbeat vs Cron：`/app/docs/automation/cron-vs-heartbeat.md`\n\n**如果你说“最新文档”是想看最近该从哪开始读，建议顺序：**\n1. `cli/index.md`\n2. `cli/configure.md`\n3. `cli/gateway.md`\n4. `channels/index.md`\n5. `automation/cron-jobs.md`\n\n刚才我也试了联网搜索，但当前 `web_search` 没配 Brave API key，所以我改用本地文档源查了。\n\n如果你要，我可以下一步直接帮你：\n- 读一遍并总结 **OpenClaw 最新文档重点**\n- 或者只看某块：**安装 / 配置 / 渠道接入 / 自动化 / 搜索**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":892,"output":350,"cacheRead":36864,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38106,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773255205738}}
{"type":"message","id":"878c36cb","parentId":"ee3613e4","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:54:15.774Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b542febbc48a0c2951476bd3d396\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-11 18:54 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b542febbc48a0c2951476bd3d396]\nou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2: 你调用的是那个服务接口？ tavily 是下"}],"timestamp":1773255255771}}
{"type":"message","id":"3f029c36","parentId":"878c36cb","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:54:28.669Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Explaining system limitations**\n\nI’m determining whether I need to address any prior work regarding the current config or service. I think I don’t actually need to recall anything from memory. I'll clarify that I attempted a built-in web search, but it failed due to a missing key. Also, I should mention that local docs and web fetch attempts were blocked, not from Tavily. Just because a skill is installed doesn’t mean it’s actively used, and I’ll keep it concise.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"不是 Tavily。\n\n刚才我实际走的是这几步：\n\n1. **先调用内置 `web_search` 工具**\n   - 这个工具当前配置的是 **Brave Search**\n   - 返回了：`missing_brave_api_key`\n\n2. **然后我尝试 `web_fetch` 直连 docs.openclaw.ai**\n   - 但被拦了：`Blocked: resolves to private/internal/special-use IP address`\n\n3. **最后改查本地文档**\n   - 直接读 `/app/docs`\n\n所以这次真正用到的是：\n\n- `web_search` → **Brave Search 接口**（但没 key，没成功）\n- `web_fetch` → 普通网页抓取（也没成功）\n- `exec` → 查本地 `/app/docs`\n\n**不是 Tavily。**\n\n你前面装的 `web-search-pro` 只是**技能**，不等于底层搜索接口自动变成 Tavily。  \n技能更像一套“什么时候用、怎么用”的说明；真正底层能不能走 Tavily，取决于：\n\n- 是否装了对应 Tavily 技能/集成\n- 是否配置了 Tavily API key\n- 该技能的 SKILL.md 里是否明确指向 Tavily\n\n如果你要，我现在可以直接帮你看：\n- `web-search-pro` 这个技能内部到底写的是啥\n- 它是不是走 Tavily\n- 还是走 Brave / DuckDuckGo / Exa / 其他接口"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":981,"output":440,"cacheRead":37376,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38797,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773255255773}}
{"type":"message","id":"51ec77fc","parentId":"3f029c36","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:54:53.989Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b542fe91830a4c4eb2c87cc4fcdc\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-11 18:54 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b542fe91830a4c4eb2c87cc4fcdc]\nou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2: 调用web-search-pro 技能搜索"}],"timestamp":1773255293986}}
{"type":"message","id":"fa5f4c50","parentId":"51ec77fc","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:54:59.951Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_gcGDP7FuBXFWMpDRW49uLPdz","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace/skills/web-search-pro/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":671,"output":252,"cacheRead":38272,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39195,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773255293987}}
{"type":"message","id":"20604093","parentId":"fa5f4c50","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:54:59.972Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_gcGDP7FuBXFWMpDRW49uLPdz","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: web-search-pro\ndescription: |\n  Multi-engine web search with full parameter control. Supports Tavily, Exa, Serper, and SerpAPI\n  with domain filtering, date ranges, deep search, news mode, and content extraction.\n  Auto-selects the best engine based on query type and available API keys.\n  多引擎精细化搜索：支持域名过滤、日期范围、深度搜索、新闻模式、内容提取。\n  根据查询类型和可用 API Key 自动选择最优引擎。\nhomepage: https://github.com/Zjianru/web-search-pro\nmetadata:\n  openclaw:\n    emoji: \"🔎\"\n    always: true\n    requires:\n      bins: [\"node\"]\n      env: [\"TAVILY_API_KEY\"]\n    primaryEnv: \"TAVILY_API_KEY\"\n---\n\n# Web Search Pro\n\nMulti-engine web search with full parameter control for AI agents.\nA precision supplement to OpenClaw's built-in `web_search` (Brave/Perplexity), providing\ndomain filtering, deep search, news mode, date ranges, and content extraction\nthat the built-in search does not support.\n\n多引擎精细化网络搜索，为 AI Agent 设计。\n作为 OpenClaw 内置 `web_search`（Brave/Perplexity）的精细化补充，提供域名过滤、\n深度搜索、新闻模式、日期范围、内容提取等内置搜索不支持的能力。\n配置一个或多个 API Key，自动选择最优引擎。\n\n## Engines / 引擎\n\n| Engine | Strengths | Free Tier | API Key Env |\n|--------|-----------|-----------|-------------|\n| **Tavily** | AI-optimized, best answer quality, full filters, extract | 1000/month | `TAVILY_API_KEY` |\n| **Exa** | Semantic/neural search, deep research | $10 credit | `EXA_API_KEY` |\n| **Serper** | Real Google SERP, best news coverage | 100/month | `SERPER_API_KEY` |\n| **SerpAPI** | Multi-engine (Google/Bing/Baidu/Yandex/DuckDuckGo) | 250/month | `SERPAPI_API_KEY` |\n\n## Auto-Select Priority / 自动选择优先级\n\nWhen `--engine` is not specified, the skill picks the best available engine:\n\n| Query Type | Priority | Reason |\n|------------|----------|--------|\n| Default | Tavily > Exa > Serper > SerpAPI | Tavily has best AI answer + full filters |\n| `--deep` | Tavily > Exa | Both have dedicated deep search modes |\n| `--news` | Serper > Tavily | Google News has widest coverage |\n| `--news --days` | Tavily only | `--days` is Tavily news-specific parameter |\n| `--include-domains` | Tavily > Exa > Serper > SerpAPI | Tavily/Exa have native domain filters |\n| `--search-engine baidu` | SerpAPI | Only SerpAPI supports Baidu/Yandex |\n\n## Search / 搜索\n\n```bash\n# Basic search (auto-select engine)\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/search.mjs \"query\"\n\n# Force specific engine\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/search.mjs \"query\" --engine tavily\n\n# Domain filtering (only search specific sites)\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/search.mjs \"query\" --include-domains \"github.com,stackoverflow.com\"\n\n# Exclude domains\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/search.mjs \"query\" --exclude-domains \"pinterest.com,quora.com\"\n\n# Date range (absolute)\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/search.mjs \"query\" --from 2026-01-01 --to 2026-02-09\n\n# Time range (relative)\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/search.mjs \"query\" --time-range week\n\n# Deep/advanced search\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/search.mjs \"query\" --deep\n\n# News search\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/search.mjs \"query\" --news --days 7\n\n# Multi-engine: Baidu search\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/search.mjs \"query\" --engine serpapi --search-engine baidu\n\n# More results\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/search.mjs \"query\" -n 10\n\n# JSON output (for programmatic use)\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/search.mjs \"query\" --json\n```\n\n## Extract / 内容提取\n\nExtract readable content from URLs (Tavily Extract or Exa livecrawl):\n\n```bash\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/extract.mjs \"https://example.com/article\"\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/extract.mjs \"url1\" \"url2\" \"url3\"\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/extract.mjs \"url\" --engine exa\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/extract.mjs \"url\" --json\n```\n\n## All Options / 全部参数\n\n| Option | Description | Engines |\n|--------|-------------|---------|\n| `--engine <name>` | Force engine: tavily\\|exa\\|serper\\|serpapi | all |\n| `-n <count>` | Number of results (default: 5) | all |\n| `--deep` | Deep/advanced search mode | tavily, exa |\n| `--news` | News search mode | tavily, serper, serpapi |\n| `--days <n>` | Limit news to last N days | tavily |\n| `--include-domains <d,...>` | Only search these domains | all (native: tavily, exa) |\n| `--exclude-domains <d,...>` | Exclude these domains | all (native: tavily, exa) |\n| `--time-range <range>` | day\\|week\\|month\\|year | all |\n| `--from <YYYY-MM-DD>` | Results after this date | all |\n| `--to <YYYY-MM-DD>` | Results before this date | all |\n| `--search-engine <name>` | SerpAPI sub-engine: google\\|bing\\|baidu\\|yandex\\|duckduckgo | serpapi |\n| `--country <code>` | Country code (us, cn, de...) | serper, serpapi |\n| `--lang <code>` | Language code (en, zh, de...) | serper, serpapi |\n| `--json` | Raw JSON output | all |\n\n## Setup / 配置\n\nAdd API keys to your environment (e.g., `~/.openclaw/.env`):\n\n```bash\n# Configure at least one (recommended: Tavily)\nTAVILY_API_KEY=tvly-xxxxx        # https://tavily.com (1000 free/month)\nEXA_API_KEY=exa-xxxxx            # https://exa.ai ($10 free credit)\nSERPER_API_KEY=xxxxx             # https://serper.dev (100 free/month)\nSERPAPI_API_KEY=xxxxx            # https://serpapi.com (250 free/month)\n```\n\n## Notes / 说明\n\n- At least one API key must be configured\n- Metadata declares runtime prerequisites explicitly:\n  - `requires.bins`: `node`\n  - `requires.env`: `TAVILY_API_KEY` (primary onboarding key)\n  - `primaryEnv`: `TAVILY_API_KEY`\n- Other provider keys (`EXA_API_KEY`, `SERPER_API_KEY`, `SERPAPI_API_KEY`) are optional and used when `--engine`/auto-select routes to those engines\n- `--search-engine <name>` always uses SerpAPI and requires `SERPAPI_API_KEY`\n- `--deep` only works on Tavily/Exa; if both keys are missing, command exits with an error\n- `--news` only works on Tavily/Serper/SerpAPI; if none are available, command exits with an error\n- `--days` only works with Tavily news mode\n- `--news --days <n>` auto-selects Tavily; if Tavily key is missing, command exits with an error\n- Domain filtering via `--include-domains`/`--exclude-domains` works natively on Tavily and Exa; on Serper/SerpAPI it's implemented via `site:` query operators\n- `--deep` mode uses more API credits (Tavily: 2x, Exa: varies)\n- Extract only works with Tavily and Exa\n- Missing/invalid option values fail fast with explicit CLI error messages (no silent fallback, no runtime TypeError)\n- All output is Markdown-formatted for AI agent consumption; use `--json` for programmatic access\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773255299966}}
{"type":"message","id":"cbc506d6","parentId":"20604093","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:55:07.133Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"技能说明表明需要TAVILY_API_KEY至少。用户要我调用这个技能搜索。先检查环境变量是否有 key，若没有则说明无法调用。用 exec 运行该脚本也可以。先看目录。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ixzzf9ZjyivnQGlLnjvrwTBU","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /home/node/.openclaw/workspace/skills/web-search-pro && find /home/node/.openclaw/workspace/skills/web-search-pro -maxdepth 2 -type f | sort","workdir":"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":2054,"output":128,"cacheRead":38784,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40966,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773255299969}}
