{"type":"message","id":"5e946518","parentId":"9019cb1d","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:55:34.676Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_Mvdm0JO5mrWI7DF22KUHnSnD","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Search: OpenClaw latest documentation\n**Engine**: tavily\n\n### Answer\n\nOpenClaw is a self-hosted AI assistant that connects to messaging platforms. The latest documentation is available at https://docs.z.ai/devpack/tool/openclaw and https://docs.openclaw.ai.\n\n---\n\n### Results (5)\n\n- **OpenClaw - Overview - Z.AI DEVELOPER DOCUMENT** (73%)\n  https://docs.z.ai/devpack/tool/openclaw\n  OpenClaw is a personal AI assistant that runs on your own devices and connects to various messaging platforms. It can be configured to use Z.AI's GLM models\n\n- **OpenClaw AI/ML - AI/ML API Documentation** (72%)\n  https://docs.aimlapi.com/quickstart/openclaw\n  OpenClaw is an AI platform for building AI agents and assistants. It runs on your own devices and connects to popular messaging platforms\n\n- **The ULTIMATE OpenClaw Setup Guide! : r/AiForSmallBusiness** (70%)\n  https://www.reddit.com/r/AiForSmallBusiness/comments/1r4uyrh/the_ultimate_openclaw_setup_guide/\n  - **Official Docs**: https://docs.openclaw.ai (super detailed!) - **GitHub**: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw (see the code!)\n\n- **OpenClaw | Docs** (70%)\n  https://docs.cortecs.ai/integration-examples/openclaw\n  OpenClaw is a self-hosted solution that lets you interact with your personal assistants from anywhere, keeping infrastructure under your control\n\n- **OpenClaw Documentation — Complete Setup & User Guide** (68%)\n  https://www.getopenclaw.ai/docs\n  OpenClaw documentation with step-by-step tutorials. Installation guide, configuration reference, channel setup (WhatsApp, Telegram,"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":7142,"aggregated":"## Search: OpenClaw latest documentation\n**Engine**: tavily\n\n### Answer\n\nOpenClaw is a self-hosted AI assistant that connects to messaging platforms. The latest documentation is available at https://docs.z.ai/devpack/tool/openclaw and https://docs.openclaw.ai.\n\n---\n\n### Results (5)\n\n- **OpenClaw - Overview - Z.AI DEVELOPER DOCUMENT** (73%)\n  https://docs.z.ai/devpack/tool/openclaw\n  OpenClaw is a personal AI assistant that runs on your own devices and connects to various messaging platforms. It can be configured to use Z.AI's GLM models\n\n- **OpenClaw AI/ML - AI/ML API Documentation** (72%)\n  https://docs.aimlapi.com/quickstart/openclaw\n  OpenClaw is an AI platform for building AI agents and assistants. It runs on your own devices and connects to popular messaging platforms\n\n- **The ULTIMATE OpenClaw Setup Guide! : r/AiForSmallBusiness** (70%)\n  https://www.reddit.com/r/AiForSmallBusiness/comments/1r4uyrh/the_ultimate_openclaw_setup_guide/\n  - **Official Docs**: https://docs.openclaw.ai (super detailed!) - **GitHub**: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw (see the code!)\n\n- **OpenClaw | Docs** (70%)\n  https://docs.cortecs.ai/integration-examples/openclaw\n  OpenClaw is a self-hosted solution that lets you interact with your personal assistants from anywhere, keeping infrastructure under your control\n\n- **OpenClaw Documentation — Complete Setup & User Guide** (68%)\n  https://www.getopenclaw.ai/docs\n  OpenClaw documentation with step-by-step tutorials. Installation guide, configuration reference, channel setup (WhatsApp, Telegram,","cwd":"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773255334667}}
