{"type":"message","id":"d4448486","parentId":"20a1c6e9","timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:10:29.403Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"那就能用。\n\n以后你如果说这类话，我就该走 `mcporter`：\n\n- `列一下 MCP server`\n- `看这个 server 有哪些 tools`\n- `调用某个 MCP tool`\n- `给这个 MCP 服务做 auth`\n- `看 / 改 mcporter 配置`\n- `启动或检查 mcporter daemon`\n\n你要的话，我现在就可以直接：\n- 列当前 MCP servers\n- 或调用一个你指定的 MCP tool"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":366,"output":103,"cacheRead":71040,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71509,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773256221010}}
