{"type":"message","id":"d6bb3175","parentId":"f13249dc","timestamp":"2026-03-11T23:01:19.802Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在我这边能看到的已启用频道只有：\n\n- **Feishu**：ON\n\n也就是你现在正在用的这个。\n\n如果你问的是 **OpenClaw 支持哪些频道**，它支持的不止这个，文档里有这些常见的：\n\n- Telegram\n- WhatsApp\n- Discord\n- Slack\n- Signal\n- iMessage\n- IRC\n- Google Chat\n- Line\n- Feishu\n- 还有一些别的\n\n但**当前这台机器实际开着的**，只有 **Feishu**。\n\n如果你要，我可以继续帮你：\n- 查这台机器支持的全部 channel 配置\n- 或看看怎么再开一个 Telegram / Discord / Signal"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1305,"output":155,"cacheRead":72064,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73524,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773270060705}}
{"type":"message","id":"456d35ba","parentId":"d6bb3175","timestamp":"2026-03-11T23:20:21.979Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b542bc59d68a0b4b57770fca42ce\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-11 23:20 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b542bc59d68a0b4b57770fca42ce]\nou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2: 那些时候中国用"}],"timestamp":1773271221972}}
{"type":"message","id":"0e8f5a46","parentId":"456d35ba","timestamp":"2026-03-11T23:20:36.617Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering usable channels in China**\n\nIt seems the user is asking about which communication channels can be used in China. I don't think I need to remember this information since it’s current factual advice. I could mention options like Feishu and Telegram, but I should note that Telegram is blocked in mainland China. WhatsApp and Discord are also unavailable. I want to make sure my answer is clear and concise for the user!\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"在中国大陆，实际好用的我会这么分：\n\n## 相对好用\n- **Feishu（飞书）**  \n  最稳，国内环境友好，你现在这个就是。\n\n- **企业微信**  \n  如果 OpenClaw 有对应接法的话，也会比海外 IM 更适合国内环境。  \n  但你这台现在没开这个。\n\n## 能用但看网络环境\n- **Telegram**  \n  功能很好，但在中国大陆通常需要代理。\n\n- **Discord**  \n  一样，通常要代理。\n\n- **Signal / WhatsApp**\n  也基本都依赖代理，国内直连不稳定。\n\n## 不太适合国内日常主用\n- **IRC / Slack / Google Chat / Line / iMessage bridge**\n  不是不能用，是要么场景偏窄，要么接入成本高，要么国内使用习惯不强。\n\n## 直接结论\n如果你问“**在中国用哪个最省心**”：\n\n**首选就是 Feishu。**\n\n如果你想要第二个备选，我会看你需求：\n- **工作协作**：Feishu\n- **极客/海外社群联动**：Telegram / Discord（但要代理）\n- **个人稳定主通道**：还是 Feishu 最实际\n\n如果你愿意，我可以直接帮你排个序，按你这个环境给出：\n**中国可用频道推荐 Top 3**。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":435,"output":420,"cacheRead":73344,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74199,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773271221977}}
{"type":"message","id":"7e5839cb","parentId":"0e8f5a46","timestamp":"2026-03-11T23:57:23.432Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b541458eb50a8b3fb4e737c8b1b8\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-11 23:57 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b541458eb50a8b3fb4e737c8b1b8]\nou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2: 多端"}],"timestamp":1773273443427}}
{"type":"message","id":"0c73d51c","parentId":"7e5839cb","timestamp":"2026-03-11T23:57:40.512Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Clarifying multi-device inquiry**\n\nIt looks like the user is asking about \"多端,\" which probably means multi-device. I don't think I need any specific tools for this. I'll explore what multi-device capabilities could involve and prepare an informative answer for the user. I want to ensure that I accurately address their question about how various devices interact or function together. Making sure I'm thorough will help them understand the concept better!\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"如果你说的是 **“多端同时用”**，那在中国我会这么看：\n\n## 最适合多端的\n### 1. Feishu\n这个最省心。\n\n原因很简单：\n- 手机、电脑、网页都成熟\n- 国内网络环境友好\n- 消息同步稳定\n- 你工作和日常切换也方便\n\n如果你的目标是：\n**手机能发、电脑能看、随时都能找我**\n那飞书就是最实际的。\n\n---\n\n## 也算多端，但有前提\n### 2. Telegram\n优点：\n- 多端体验很好\n- 桌面端、移动端、网页端都不错\n- 机器人生态成熟\n\n问题：\n- 在中国大陆基本离不开代理\n- 稳定性取决于你的网络环境\n\n所以它是：\n**产品层面多端很好，国内现实层面没飞书省心。**\n\n---\n\n### 3. Discord\n也是多端，但更偏社区，不像飞书那么适合“日常个人助理入口”。\n\n优点：\n- 桌面端、移动端都行\n- Bot 能力强\n\n问题：\n- 国内同样吃网络\n- 私聊型使用没飞书顺手\n\n---\n\n## 不太推荐当“多端主入口”的\n### WhatsApp / Signal\n不是说不能多端，而是：\n- 国内环境不友好\n- 接入和长期稳定性一般\n- 当主通道不如飞书省事\n\n---\n\n## 直接结论\n\n如果你在意的是 **中国环境 + 多端同步 + 稳定使用**：\n\n**第一名就是 Feishu。**\n\n如果你在意的是 **功能生态 + 多端体验**，并且你本来就有稳定代理：\n- Telegram 可以当第二选择\n\n---\n\n## 我给你的实际建议\n\n### 最稳方案\n- **主通道：Feishu**\n- 其他先别折腾\n\n### 如果你想双通道\n- **国内主用：Feishu**\n- **备用/海外：Telegram**\n\n这样最合理。\n\n如果你要，我可以接着直接帮你回答下一层：\n\n- **多端里哪个最适合做“主号”**\n- **Feishu + Telegram 双通道怎么配**\n- **OpenClaw 适不适合一人开多个频道同时接入**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":72817,"output":551,"cacheRead":1536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74904,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773273443429}}
